    <section id="postingbody">
        <div class="print-information print-qrcode-container">
            <p class="print-qrcode-label">QR Code Link to This Post</p>
            <div class="print-qrcode" data-location="http://newyork.craigslist.org/que/ret/6036332081.html"></div>
        </div>
We are hiring for retail sales associates in our electronic retail stores in JFK in NY, NY. These are direct hire roles with the Corporation and have great long term, career advancement if desired. <br>
<br>
If you meet all the qualifications below and are interested with self drive and a natural conversationist, please respond with your resume ASAP in a Word document. These are immediate starts with the holiday season approaching. <br>
Bilingual is a must<br>
Must be outgoing and self driven and able to engage customers to achieve sales goals<br>
Standing role..no sitting<br>
YOU MUST BE ABLE TO PASS a EXTENSIVE TSA background criminal check<br>
<br>
Hours: 20-30 to start(gain more with seniority) <br>
*MUST be flexible with hours of opening and closing and able work weekend hours <br>
Pay: $11 an hr plus end of month bonus pay based on goals met and incentive plans<br>
*Benefits, PTO, etc for employees whom work over 30 hours a week<br>
<br>
Requirements:<br>
Excellent candidates bring the following skills to the team:<br>
-Sales aptitude and ability to proactively engage customers.<br>
-Strong motivation to be challenged and hit personal and company sales targets.<br>
-Able and willing to work some evenings, weekends and holidays.<br>
-Outgoing personality and ability to speak with brand new customers daily.<br>
-Strong desire to learn and take on new responsibilities.<br>
-Ability to stand on your feet for an entire day/shift.<br>
-Able to lift/move up to 50 pounds.<br>
Sales experience preferably in the retail industry and with high end products.<br>
-High school degree or equivalent.<br>
-Computer skills (Microsoft products).<br>
-Must successfully pass airport and the company background checks. <br>
<br>
Benefits<br>
Our energetic market is filled with passengers needing and wanting the best electronics and accessories. This dynamic sales environment offers:<br>
<br>
- Competitive base salary<br>
<br>
- Generous employee discount program<br>
<br>
- Discounts with our partners<br>
<br>
- Monthly bonus program<br>
<br>
- Continuous training and support<br>
<br>
- Numerous contests and incentives<br>
<br>
- Referral bonus program<br>
<br>
    </section>

